text: Phillip W. Williams Jr. (born March 20, 1965 in Fort Monmouth, New Jersey) is a Republican politician in the US state of Alabama. He was a member of the Alabama Senate, representing the 10th District, from 2010 until 2019. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Alabama state senators Category:Alabama Republicans Category:University of South Alabama alumni Category:Birmingham School of Law alumni Category:People from Monmouth County, New Jersey Category:21st-century American politicians
title: Phil Williams (Alabama senator)
